{"tid":187581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中資入侵】 「滴滴出行」擬投專營的士！業界狂呻：投資額過億 車行冇得鬥","createTime":"2017-04-05T05:26:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-06T00:56:46.000Z","uid":39464,"like":12,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9208db74f32edfe51967efe25898bec936bafb0f","tid":187581,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T05:26:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170405/large/1491358333_2cc2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170405%2Flarge%2F1491358333_2cc2.jpg&h=e6183223&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 【新增滴滴出行回應】政府早前建議推出600架專營的士，分3個專營權供業界競投。業界粗略統計，第一筆投資金額至少過億元，一般車行根本無能力承受。<br />\n<br />\n《明報》引消息指，內地「滴滴出行」近日已接觸業界，為競投本港專營的士「摸底」。報道指，「滴滴出行」此舉，一來關心港府推動專營的士是否成功，尤其早前的士業界成立了「撤回的士專營權大聯盟」，曾有的士堵塞立法會及政府總部一帶道路的行動，二來了解香港有哪些公司有興趣競投專營的士，以評估自己的勝算。<br />\n<br />\n「滴滴出行」發言人向本報回應，並無否認向業界「摸底」競投專營的士的傳聞，並指公司扎根本港多年，致力於以技術提升本港的士服務質素及司機收入，對政府政策走向關心是自然的事，希望政策方向日益開明，有助於本港智慧城市發展，也將持續向各界持份者虛心請教與交流。<br />\n<br />\n業界質疑，政府推出專營的士計劃，似為「滴滴出行」此類財雄勢大的企業度身訂做，同時「滴滴出行」旗下「快的Taxi」早已打入香港市場，若它要競爭專營的士權，入場成本已較其他公司低。<br />\n<br />\n滴滴打車於2012年在北京開始出現，於2015年與快的打車合併，並於去年8月收購Uber中國品牌，自此獨霸中國call市場。騰訊（700）、阿里巴巴及Uber分別持有滴滴出行11.4%及10%權益。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170405/56523383\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170405%2F56523383&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2Bf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=774d6560\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170405%2F56523383&h=d55f4a6e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170405/56523383</a>"},{"pid":"6160475f3ff3ec87c531d5630f37f0f54afda832","tid":187581,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T09:08:26.000Z","msg":"而家D60後真係好唔捱得"},{"pid":"ef8170f4462303782a1e7974da16e89eedb31534","tid":187581,"uid":96854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T09:22:11.000Z","msg":"一滴滴出行係咪即係支那抄uber嗰間?"},{"pid":"71fa34a023d1e39d8aa2eabca54f57f336c0ee9e","tid":187581,"uid":14799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T09:23:30.000Z","msg":"撐政府反佔中啊嗱"},{"pid":"6595d1e8545b0ce2c24d8ff2a31f166ea7f13692","tid":187581,"uid":17832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T09:25:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7903f15d8695bbf70279cdb1a1c2520b433729fc","tid":187581,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T09:33:02.000Z","msg":"唉家下啲死廢老少少競爭都唔捱得學人講獅子山精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eb289c3e85adb863ef6c8cd040f2cfc8bac0d55","tid":187581,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T09:35:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中資鬥痰胃豬？定夾埋玩鳩渣的士佬？</blockquote><br />\n的士佬東家唔打打西家<br />\n多左車咪仲多選擇"},{"pid":"23b67017a164ca5f395807fd3cb77c1bb36d8dd8","tid":187581,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T09:35:28.000Z","msg":"佔中時申請禁制令<br />\n鬧人阻住佢地搵食<br />\n今日變紙巾"},{"pid":"8851fe76c44eea2677cd2ccb07372922061e2a50","tid":187581,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T09:36:41.000Z","msg":"無班的士佬唔好阻住滴滴搵食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"534ca700641e15ca0f16b182df7826ed4001f759","tid":187581,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T09:37:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你班的士佬唔好阻住滴滴搵食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f4c20729498d81cff9e46c8ea8f81eeda9e36dd8","tid":187581,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T09:38:05.000Z","msg":"的士狗又做咗港共condom <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48539a339e4502cd33f092878bd43567e8351c1a","tid":187581