一個舖位都比佢哋瘋狂高價搶晒， 香港人食屎呀， 到時物價貴晒都係小市民負擔"},{"pid":"e0fb378273bf0c20b0b76f8e6f39956dd20ce71b","tid":187581,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T09:54:15.000Z","msg":"廢老：一日最衰都係佔中班o靚仔"},{"pid":"fb4a325b3cc04b2124dda3aa3f652a0e26517831","tid":187581,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T09:55:01.000Z","msg":"哼，M巾嘅野係咁架啦，反佔旺佔鐘反得咁開心咪好囉，大家今日一齊咁仆街喇<br />\n<br />\n一早講左所有行業個趨勢都係紅資取代港資<br />\n<br />\n唔鐘意咪走囉，再唔係咪同中國人打工囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f02bf7de7fda5bf83fd0f5d845b4a7768a734ce","tid":187581,"uid":35491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T10:02:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>「滴滴出行」發言人向本報回應，並無否認向業界「摸底」競投專營的士的傳聞，並指公司扎根本港多年...<br />\n<br />\n滴滴打車於2012年在北京開始出現，於2015年與快的打車合併，並於去年8月收購Uber中國品牌，自此獨霸中國call市場...<br />\n<br />\n即係點？滴滴喺香港出現左好耐傢喇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n港豬有字就睇嫁啦, 點會查佢Background 呀</blockquote><br />\nd 報紙佬都係求鳩其照紙搬字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW 的士佬應該喜迎中資加入的士市場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"015a53543edd5a6a31e7f49bafad85899eb79e93","tid":187581,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T10:03:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中資滴滴vs 的士佬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又要兩篤屎揀一篤食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b68fece24496acb2101a789c355500232856a4e8","tid":187581,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T10:05:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5df957fccb64168e23e4990cd086da38de286eec","tid":187581,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T10:19:14.000Z","msg":"的士佬喜迎融合，加強競爭力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1cdcae6c953be598eb57ce7924d9e07046ed487","tid":187581,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T10:19:56.000Z","msg":"班垃圾的士佬是要管的！"},{"pid":"4d2278147072f9e2de31ae0de3599ae0daccbae4","tid":187581,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T10:22:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實得600部都唔會好大影響啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n600只係打頭陣"},{"pid":"e5004ee98469ea72ad5cd29ae3eb1b5169c9e1d4","tid":187581,"uid":93640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T10:23:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>的士佬喜迎融合，加強競爭力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n反對姐係唔合作，係到搞搞震，破壞社會穩定、破壞香港法治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b6b7a34b818a92f46e026aa4bc266bce0e77f83","tid":187581,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T10:23:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/967sjzhy\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F967sjzhy&h=90a950ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"331177bed22e5efa9d2a3a473caa1b335c7d816a","tid":187581,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T10:24:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9caace62933cfb9d3bc7ab9b7b06fb44fe2c1220","tid":187581,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T10:25:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「滴滴出行」發言人向本報回應，並無否認向業界「摸底」競投專營的士的傳聞，並指公司扎根本港多年...<br />\n<br />\n滴滴打車於2012年在北京開始出現，於2015年與快的打車合併，並於去年8月收購Uber中國品牌，自此獨霸中國call市場...<br />\n<br />\n即係點？滴滴喺香港出現左好耐傢喇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n公司註冊處查冊睇過同「滴滴」有關而又可能同「的士」業務有關嘅公司，最舊嘅成立年份為2013年<br />\n<br />\n不過都係e-commerce野